    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799160/extras/001b3f072af205980e616f5816290509.avif?t=1637045477\" width=600 height=72 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799160/extras/eaa1e72b7e9331b739dbbd69955cb86a.poster.avif?t=1637045477\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799160/extras/eaa1e72b7e9331b739dbbd69955cb86a.webm?t=1637045477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799160/extras/eaa1e72b7e9331b739dbbd69955cb86a.mp4?t=1637045477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A math puzzle game with matchsticks where your mind will be constantly challenged after each level.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Move, add or remove sticks to obtain the correct answer before you run out of moves.<br></li><li> Math puzzles with addition, subtraction, multiplication, division, square root and much more.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799160/extras/a886374a93611f74873d278afaddb847.avif?t=1637045477\" width=600 height=72 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799160/extras/29b4e91ed8e4df97c888b932f0d23941.poster.avif?t=1637045477\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799160/extras/29b4e91ed8e4df97c888b932f0d23941.webm?t=1637045477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799160/extras/29b4e91ed8e4df97c888b932f0d23941.mp4?t=1637045477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> No time, no score, no pressure! Take your time at each level.<br></li><li> 60 carefully selected puzzles.<br></li><li> Practice your memory, logical and spatial thinking.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799160/extras/e09d22079672338abc959e98665b50c2.avif?t=1637045477\" width=600 height=72 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799160/extras/cb2f5be9926966b00205358be63e8c2b.poster.avif?t=1637045477\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799160/extras/cb2f5be9926966b00205358be63e8c2b.webm?t=1637045477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799160/extras/cb2f5be9926966b00205358be63e8c2b.mp4?t=1637045477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 3 beautiful and original themes to be selected<br></li><li> Original soundtrack exclusive to this game, by Tatyana Jacques<br></li><li> Coding and development by the programmer Alexander Froelich </li></ul>",
